title: Overcoming Obstacles With SPUNK!
description: Break through your barriers with SPUNK! Are you ready to break through the barriers obstructing your goals and move into a position of leadership? Then do so with SPUNK! Learn the steps required to overcome obstacles and become an effective and dynamic leader. The five Keys guide you Developing a positive attitude Learning people skills Raising self-esteem Overcoming fears Setting goals Joined by authors David Ambrose, p.m. terrell, Darlene Wofford, Jocelyn Andersen, Bob Johnson, C. Denise Sutton, and Bill Wilson, Wolfe’s “Overcoming Obstacles with SPUNK! The Keys to Leadership & Goal-Setting” will energize your passion for life! A professional speaker trained in a top motivation education system, Wolfe helps people develop passion, confidence, and an image of success. Known as “Spunk On A Stick”, the author resides in North Carolina with her husband and two cats. “With a positive attitude, any goal can be achieved!”
author: L. Diane Wolfe
